# GitHub Upload Checklist

1. Extract the ZIP.
2. Open the extracted folder.
3. Select all files inside the folder.
4. Drag them into GitHub using `Add file > Upload files`.
5. Commit directly to `main`.
6. Wait for the Pages deployment to complete under `Actions`.
7. Hard refresh the staging site with `Ctrl + F5`.

The repository root must contain `index.html` directly.
